[center][img]http://img864.imageshack.us/img864/1628/splashwi.png[/img][/center] [center]I Changed server name to InFecTionX[/center] [center]Project-InFecTion[/center] [center]LeT The HaXx BeGin[/center] InTroducTion Let me start off by saying that Project-InFecTion is a project that I have been working for a long time. Project-InFecTion was created on May 25th, it however was never released to the public. I have been working on this server alone as I have not found anyone capable to help me. Now, I am not the best coder in the world, so I do need help in making Project-InFecTion into the server I have dreampt about. So I come here today to as you guys to help me into making Project-InFecTion into the "Perfect" server. [center][img]http://img853.imageshack.us/img853/8639/informationf.jpg[/img][/center]
-Hand Cannon working perfectly. -All spirit shields working perfectly with correct effects. -Torva armour working perfectly with correct effects. -All specials including Vls, Swh, Claws, Dbow, etc.. are 100% -Combat is amazing. -Soulsplit actually working. -Turmoil working perfectly. -FullScreen. -New Rs trade interface. -Karosi Spec 100%. -All basic minigames, Jad, Fight Pits, Duel arena, etc.. -Switching is perfect.
Will Be added:
-Bounty Hunter (fully working.) -New Home Location. -Moving Splash screen. -Custom Jframe. -Zombie minigame.
